Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.49,1:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.03,1:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快 跑 跑 跑\NCome on, run, run, run.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.06,1:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说了要跑\Ntold you to fucking run.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.72,1:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\NJust sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.05,1:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让我帮你拔出来\NLet me...let me help pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.58,1:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,必须拔出来\NIt's gotta come out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.05,1:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我去给你找点止痛的东西\NI'm gonna find you something for the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.03,1:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh!
