Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.74,1:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得\NYou don't think?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.38,1:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不感觉\NYou don't listen?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.34,1:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所有选项摆在你面前 你偏偏次次都选最蠢的那个\NOut of all the options in front of you, you always manage to pick the dumbest one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.32,1:08:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人印象深刻\NIt's actually impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.58,1:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的\NHow do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.72,1:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你\NI saved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.81,1:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来可以自救的\NYou could have saved yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.04,1:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以去找救援\NYou could have gotten help.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.70,1:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我照顾不了我们俩\NI can't take care of both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.52,1:08:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的做不到\NI can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.56,1:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 都是我的错\NOh, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.30,1:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.54,1:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个累赘\NI'm such a burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.28,1:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是个孩子\NYou're a fucking child!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.28,1:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈来这里唯一的原因就是你\NThe only reason I'm fucking here is because of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.02,1:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在我他妈要死在这里也是因为你\Nand now I'm gonna fucking die here because of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.44,1:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我 你几小时前就死了\NYou would have died hours ago if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.78,1:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 抱歉我没跑掉把你扔下 但这事儿更像你的作风\NOh, I'm sorry I didn't run away and abandon you, but that's more your thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.90,1:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开是对的\NI was right to fucking leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.22,1:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你他妈从没找到我\NAnd I wish you never goddamn found me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.21,1:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.22,1:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该跑的\NI should have run.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.05,1:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.69,1:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧\NAnd fuck off.
