Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.93,1:10:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们掌管着警察\NWe own the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.70,1:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\NGoddammit!
