Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.68,1:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的求婚\NI accept your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.05,1:21:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.89,1:21:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.64,1:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay, Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.84,1:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.14,1:21:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先得到一些保证 这样我才放心\NI'm going to need some assurances first so I know
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.41,1:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我出来的时候 你可别把我们俩都杀了\Nyou're not just going to kill us both when I come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.36,1:21:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你发誓...哦 别向我发誓\NI swear to you... Oh, don't swear to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.73,1:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的白痴\NFucking shit for brains!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.94,1:21:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,向勒贝尔先生发誓\NSwear to Mr. LeBail!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.32,1:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我向勒贝尔先生发誓 不会伤害你或你妹妹\NI swear to Mr. LeBail that no harm shall come to you or your sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.28,1:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能\NYou can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.99,1:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.84,1:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让人把你需要的一切都拿来\NI'll have everything you need brought in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.04,1:22:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备\NGet ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.99,1:22:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,参加加冕典礼的宾客已经陆续抵达\NThe guests are already arriving for coronation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.10,1:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们不妨干杯庆祝一下\NI thought maybe we could have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.45,1:23:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要成为一家人了\NWe're about to become family.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.16,1:24:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我从没想伤害你\NGrace, I never wanted to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.96,1:24:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我必须遵守规则\NBut I had to follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.68,1:24:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我们时间不多了\NListen, we don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.98,1:24:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就直说了\NSo I'm just gonna say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.62,1:24:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕\NI'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.43,1:24:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥\NIt's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.95,1:24:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI didn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.53,1:24:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底是谁\Nwho he really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.10,1:24:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了一辈子\NI spent my whole life...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.04,1:24:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找他身上的优点\Nsearching for the good in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.69,1:24:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我找到了什么\NYou know what I found?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.73,1:24:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈什么也没有\NAbsolutely fucking nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.16,1:24:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我能控制住他\NI thought I could keep him in check.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.41,1:24:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已经失控了\NBut he's lost it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.79,1:24:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我需要你的帮助\NGrace, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.96,1:24:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须一起努力控制他\NWe have to try to control him together.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.51,1:24:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有一个席位不见得就是坏事\NHaving a seat doesn't have to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.14,1:25:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想想我们能用那种权力做多少好事\NThink about all the good we could do with that power.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.98,1:25:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要你在我身边\NBut I need you at my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.36,1:25:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 格蕾丝\NHey, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.43,1:25:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像我们\NYou're not like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.69,1:25:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你有希望\NYou have hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.17,1:25:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在没有\NI don't now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.92,1:25:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是你夺走了它\NYou took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.21,1:25:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很擅长这个\NWe are good at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.78,1:25:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来点姐妹时间\NA little girl time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.40,1:26:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你让我看清了你的真面目\NThank you for showing me who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.55,1:26:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 听我解释...\NTitus, it's not a ...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.00,1:26:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 停下\NTitus, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.54,1:26:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你想控制我\NYou want to control me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.90,1:26:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.77,1:26:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要所有的权力\NYou want all the power for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.22,1:26:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.72,1:26:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想\NYou do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.48,1:26:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这么想的\NYou do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.08,1:26:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样\NYou always do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.10,1:26:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样\NYou always do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.00,1:26:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 停下 求你了\NTitus stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.08,1:26:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我 格蕾丝\NLook at me, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.40,1:26:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我 格蕾丝\NGrace, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.52,1:26:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次 还是看着我\NAnother take or look at me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.02,1:26:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到这个 格蕾丝\NI want you to see this, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.88,1:26:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到这个\NI want you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.00,1:26:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\NGrace!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.00,1:26:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到我是谁\NI want you to see who I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.38,1:26:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看清楚 我不是一个可以被人掌控的人\NI want you to see that I am not a man who can be controlled.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.94,1:26:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你提到了规则\NYou mentioned the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.38,1:26:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,规则里没有关于杀害家族成员的内容\NThere's nothing in the rules about killing a family member.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.87,1:26:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来试试控制我啊\NTry to keep me in check now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.18,1:27:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看\NJust try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.37,1:27:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 会是我抓住你\NI told you it would be me who got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.55,1:27:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们祭坛见\NI'll see you at the altar.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.19,1:29:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能...这么做\NYou can't...do this
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.45,1:29:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须这么做\NI have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.94,1:29:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有别的办法\NThere's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.91,1:29:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.84,1:30:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢姆·汉普拉\NShem HaMephorash!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.42,1:30:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈什么都看不见\NI can't see shit move.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.68,1:30:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,至高无上的撒旦路西法之名\NNomine satani Lucifer excelsis.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.18,1:30:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奉我们伟大而永恒的恩主之名\NIn the name of our great and eternal benefactor,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.49,1:30:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请现身 赐福予众人\Ncome forth and bestow your blessing upon these.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.78,1:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,以撒旦 路西法 巴利尔 利维坦之名 现身并作证\NIn the names of Satan, Lucifer, Baliel, Leviathan, come forth and bear witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.48,1:30:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.88,1:30:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.01,1:30:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 各位\NWelcome, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.24,1:30:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴有这么多人能来\NI'm pleased so many of you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.60,1:30:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅在这个美好的早晨举行加冕仪式 我们还有一场婚礼\NNot only do we have our coronation this fine morning, we also have a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.90,1:30:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的福杯满盈\NOur cup runneth over.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.12,1:31:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯\NTitus.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.07,1:31:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请伸出你的手\NYour hand, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.13,1:32:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你们的誓言是出于本意 且受撒旦之力所驱使\NYour vows being made by intent, by the power of Satan,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.96,1:32:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在宣布你们彼此归属\NI now confer the possession of each other upon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.81,1:32:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯·切斯特·丹福斯\NTitus Chester Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.92,1:32:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意娶这位女士 并承诺与她共度今生与来世吗？\NDo you take this woman, in this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.77,1:32:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是下地狱的烈火？\NUnto the fires of hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.96,1:32:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.14,1:32:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而你 格蕾丝·伊丽莎白·麦考利·勒多马斯 愿意接受这个男人\NAnd do you, Grace Elizabeth MacCaullay Le Domas, take this man to be yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.72,1:32:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在肉体和精神上 并承诺与他共度今生与来世吗？\NIn flesh and spirit, in this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.26,1:32:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是下地狱的烈火？\NUnto the fires of hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.59,1:32:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.03,1:32:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他在地狱中锻造之物 任凭凡人休想拆解\NWhat he hath forged in hell, let no mortal tear asunder.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.57,1:32:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 我们奉你的名祈求\NWe ask this in thy name, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.48,1:33:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在宣布你们结为夫妻\NI now pronounce you man and wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.08,1:33:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以亲吻新娘了\NYou may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.14,1:33:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯·丹福斯 特此授予利贝西亚议会至高席位\NTitus Danforth, is hereby granted the high seat of the council of Libecia.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.06,1:33:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.78,1:33:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.90,1:33:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.82,1:33:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.72,1:33:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.46,1:34:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\NWhat the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.69,1:34:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死自己的家族成员不违反规则\NIt's not against the rules to kill a family member.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.50,1:34:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你的提醒\NThank you for that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.39,1:34:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是我抓住了你\NIt's me who got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.45,1:35:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈发生了什么\Nthe fuck is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.10,1:35:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下\NGet on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.08,1:35:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\NShem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.52,1:35:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\NShem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.77,1:35:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\NShem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.12,1:35:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\NShem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.90,1:35:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我可以为所欲为 对吧\NThis means I can do whatever I want, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.68,1:36:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\NThat is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.60,1:36:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哈\NHuh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.73,1:36:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以领导这个组织\NI could lead this organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.43,1:36:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以改变世界\NI could change the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.14,1:36:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 作为我担任最高委员会主席后的第一项举措\NSo as my first act as the head of your high council
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.34,1:36:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我特此宣布将我自己从\NI hereby remove myself from
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.87,1:36:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个委员会 以及这整个他妈的组织中移除\Nthe council and this entire fucking organization!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.79,1:36:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟 她可以那样做吗\NBro, can she even do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.61,1:36:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出人意料的是 章程对此几乎只字未提\NThere's surprisingly little language about this in the bylaws, since no one believed
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.27,1:36:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有人相信会有人愿意主动放弃如此大的权力\Nanyone would ever willingly give away so much power.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.55,1:36:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但然后谁得到那个该死的席位\NOkay, but then who gets the fucking seat?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.27,1:36:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明前谁戴着戒指就是谁\NWhoever's wearing the ring by dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.09,1:36:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明什么时候\NWhen's dawn?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.18,1:37:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大约三分钟后\NIn three minutes, give or take.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.61,1:37:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有议会家族还是\NBut it's just the council families or...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.53,1:37:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,严格来说任何人\NLiterally anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.07,1:37:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而你说如果黎明前没人戴戒指 勒贝尔先生会\NAnd you said if no one's wearing the ring by dawn, Mr. LeBail would be...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.71,1:37:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不高兴\NVery upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.05,1:37:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不高兴\NVery upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.57,1:37:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去吃屎吧 你们这些近亲繁殖的混蛋\NChoke on it, you inbred fucks!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.58,1:37:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 我的上帝\NI'm coming, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.34,1:37:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\NShem HaMephorash!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.99,1:37:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\NHail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.96,1:37:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开战\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.08,1:37:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,操 操 操 操\NFuck, fuck, fuck, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.43,1:38:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哇\NOh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.79,1:38:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你的\NI'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.66,1:38:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,操...\NFucking...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.14,1:38:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人把这一切付之一炬\NSomeone had to burn it all down.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.90,1:38:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你很擅长毁掉一切\NYou are good at destroying things.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.10,1:38:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你自由了\NYou're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.80,1:38:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMhm.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.82,1:38:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NSee ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.10,1:38:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.68,1:38:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀\NHi, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.40,1:38:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 对 别看那里\NHey, yeah, don't look there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.79,1:38:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟\NOops
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.93,1:40:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,操 太爽了\NFuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.74,1:40:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着 婊子们\NI'm alive, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.46,1:40:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功了\NWe made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.66,1:40:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了\NWe made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.35,1:40:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个大草\NHoly fucking shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.23,1:40:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经脱离了组织 所以才幸免于难\NI've renounced my pack, so I've been spared too!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.77,1:40:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们他妈的开派对\NLet's fucking party!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.07,1:40:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,天\NJesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.67,1:41:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,咩\NMeow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.26,1:41:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能走了吗\NCan we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.06,1:41:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咩\NMeow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.86,1:41:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.02,1:41:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 火箭筒\NHah..Rocket launcher.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.05,1:42:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快 我们走\NCome on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.96,1:42:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.30,1:42:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\NI love you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.17,1:42:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\NI missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.08,1:42:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不过你知道 以后我不必再这么想了\NYeah, well, you know, I'm not gonna have to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.00,1:42:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你会他妈烦死我的\NYou're gonna get really fucking sick of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.03,1:42:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,保证\NPromise?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.88,1:42:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.16,1:43:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么处理那只山羊\NWhat are you gonna do with the goat?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.14,1:43:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.18,1:43:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这周打算结几次婚\NHow many times are you gonna get married this week?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.00,1:43:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了\NIt's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.32,1:43:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定破纪录了\NIt's gotta be a record.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.14,1:43:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.22,1:43:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去医院\NWe're gonna go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.50,1:43:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去洗个澡\NI need a bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.62,1:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也感觉快臭了\NI stink too
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.34,1:43:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Borcolasky 原创听译校正\Nsubhd.tv
